From: kaidoho <kho237115@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 27 Dec 2019 10:08:38 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] Add Zephyr OS

---
 bfd/config.bfd                             |  8 ++++----
 binutils/testsuite/lib/binutils-common.exp |  2 ++
 config.sub                                 |  2 +-
 config/gthr.m4                             |  1 +
